<%= link_to image_tag("openproject/workflow2.png",:size => '450x500', alt: "Project Mgt"  ), class: 'centre' %>

<h5>Project Types</h5>
<p>
No Change to “Bug, “Feature”, “Support”, “Milestone” and “Phase”. 
If you decide to change these, then you will also have to reconfigure the roles and workflows, which is a large task, so not recommended.
</p>
<%= link_to image_tag("openproject/types1.png",:size => '450x500', alt: "Project Mgt"  ), class: 'centre' %>
<h5>Work Package Status</h5>
<p>
No Change to the defaults. If you change these, then you will have to revisit your 
Roles and Permissions and your workflow to enable the new status to function inside the application.
</p>
<%= link_to image_tag("openproject/workpackage1.png",:size => '450x500', alt: "Project Mgt"  ), class: 'centre' %>

